					<outline text="As with the last major release, I &lt;a href=&quot;http://scripting.com/images/2018/08/24/previousVersionsMenu.png&quot;&gt;archived&lt;/a&gt; the previous &lt;a href=&quot;http://littleoutliner.com/archive/1.7.2/&quot;&gt;version&lt;/a&gt;. There are substantial UI changes in this release, you might want to choose the time to start using the new version.  " created="Fri, 24 Aug 2018 16:06:14 GMT"/>
