					<outline text="If you want to subscribe to an RSS feed for the product, &lt;a href=&quot;http://lo.1999.io/rss.xml&quot;&gt;this is it&lt;/a&gt;. " created="Fri, 24 Aug 2018 16:25:55 GMT"/>
